ygData.messageBody:
What is the actual level of the gator? Is the ancient croc higher
level, or the same level as the rest of them? I'm 21st, is it at all
possible for me to get them now, or do I need to wait a few levels?
What size/level of a group would I need to get them?

>From: Kent Anderson <wart1@...>
>Reply-To: EQ-Clerics@onelist.com
>To: EQ-Clerics@onelist.com
>Subject: Re: [EQ-Clerics] Gator Scale Leggings
>Date: Sun, 21 Nov 1999 20:09:26 -0700
>
>They are on the ancient Croc in upper guk. His replacement spawn is
>from one to 5 gators. The necessary lvl escapes me but I'd say its 34
>solo (although a pure caster can probably do them at 30) to be safe.
>The gators won't agro so you can kill one at a time. You have to clear
>them all out before the next spawn cycle will start.
>
>They weight only .4 so they do drop your overall weight significantly.
>
>Mal
